OL,4,G2300FComedy Legends: Phyllis Diller
OL,5,     GShe was one of the first female
OL,6,     Gcomics to become a household name
OL,7,     Gin America, paving the way for
OL,8,     Gthe likes of Joan Rivers and
OL,9,     GRoseanne Barr. Barry Cryer
OL,10,     Gexplores her life.
OL,11,G0000FLes Dawson's Parisienne Adventure
OL,12,     GUrban Myths. The stand-up
OL,13,     Gcomedian flees to Paris to pursue
OL,14,     Ghis dream of becoming a novelist,
OL,15,     Gbut winds up becoming a pianist
OL,16,     Gin a brothel.
OL,17,G0030FJoan Rivers And Barbra Streisand
OL,18,     GUrban Myths. 16-year-old
OL,19,     GStreisand rehearses for an off-
OL,20,     GBroadway play, with her fur-clad,
OL,21,     Gdemanding co-star Joan Rivers.
